<!--
  Profile: Eureka Pyros NM Farm
  Authors: Zamphire
  
  Setting a NM to one will cause the bot to target the mobs that spawn that NM until the NM spawns and then fights the NM. The profile will go down the list targetting from bottom to top anything set to 1.
  So if you have to stop the profile it will start back at the top when you start it again. To avoid that, set anything you kill to 0.
  
  I also recomend using https://ffxiv-eureka.com/ to keep track of which Fates are ready to be spawned again.
  
-->

